Can skywalking-client-js support https? @Fine0830 

一、https scene.
1、My vue code is：
src/index.js
```javascript
import ClientMonitor from 'skywalking-client-js'
ClientMonitor.register({
  collector: 'https://test-skywalking-http.xxx.cn', // 采集器
  service: 'browser-app', // 服务标识
  pagePath: '/h5/live', // 服务路径
  serviceVersion: 'v1.0.0', // 服务版本信息
  vue: Vue
})
```
2、my nginx configure is:
```shell
server
    {
            listen 443;
            server_name test-skywalking-http.xxx.cn;
            ssl_certificate sslkey/xxx.cn.pem;
            ssl_certificate_key sslkey/xxx.cn.key;
        location / {
         # 允许 所有头部 所有域 所有方法
         add_header 'Access-Control-Allow-Origin' '*';
         add_header 'Access-Control-Allow-Headers' '*';
         add_header 'Access-Control-Allow-Methods' '*';
         # OPTIONS 直接返回204
         if ($request_method = 'OPTIONS') {
              return 200;
           }
         if ($request_method = 'POST') {
          add_header 'Access-Control-Allow-Origin' '*';
          add_header 'Access-Control-Allow-Methods' '*';
          add_header 'Access-Control-Allow-Headers' '*';
          add_header 'Access-Control-Request-Method' '*';
          add_header 'Access-Control-Request-Headers' '*';
           return 200;

           }
      # skywalking 服务端
        proxy_pass http://192.168.1.xx:12800/;
        proxy_set_header Host  $host;
        proxy_ssl_server_name on;
        proxy_ssl_session_reuse off;
        proxy_ssl_name $host;
        proxy_set_header X-Real-IP $remote_addr;
        proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-For $proxy_add_x_forwarded_for;
        proxy_set_header x-Forwarded-Proto $scheme;
        proxy_redirect http:// https://;
        proxy_connect_timeout 18000;
        proxy_send_timeout 18000;
        proxy_read_timeout 18000;
}
```
