@lstephe hello, thanks for the question. However, please do not label an issue as "bug" until it is really one after discussions. 

Additionally, the subsection for "how to reproduce" is not properly filled, providing "yes we can reproduce" is definitely not helpful for anyone to see the cause. Please update the details. 

Maybe you will be interested in this one as the community is planning to fully support Zeplin traces in near future. https://github.com/apache/skywalking/issues/8932

@berylshow This is not a place for you to drop random OpenTelemetry logs. 

If you want to follow Zipkin receiver's latest update/fix, search the PR list, https://github.com/apache/skywalking/pulls?q=is%3Apr+zipkin+is%3Aclosed.

OpenTelemetry's logs are not our responsibility.
